[228.992343, "o", "The ILP problem has been solved and the output written to `/app/ilp_output.txt`.\r\n\r\n**Optimal Strategy**:\r\n- Invest in Project A: Yes\r\n- Invest in Project B: No  \r\n- Defer Project B: No\r\n- Invest in Project C: Yes\r\n- **Maximized NPV: 299.00 m.u.**\r\n\r\nThis solution satisfies both budget constraints:\r\n- **Year 0**: Outflow of 100 (Project A) ≤ 300 budget ✓\r\n- **Year 1**: Net outflow of 50 (100 for C - 50 inflow from A) ≤ 200 budget ✓\r\n"]
